        "Embrace the chaos, seek creativity and stay positive." Jill understands the whirlwind of the industry but does her best to build solid relationships with each and every client. Relationships matter and so does helping people feel good about themselves. Among her presence in the salon, Jill also works Dancing with the Stars, America's Got Talent, red carpet events, oversees direction of the Beauty Coach video series, tours with Beauty Coach and is the Creative Director for the BeYOUtiful Foundation. "The payoff is seeing the smiles on my client's faces. I want them to be confident, be comfortable and to know I'm always there for them."
